Revision history for Site-Configuration

0.04    2013-04-23 23:22

	The default VO configuration directory is changed from
	/etc/vo-support to /etc/vo-support/vos, to match the
	structure of the vo-support package.

0.03    2012-06-26 14:46

	The modules have been extensively refactored to be properly
	Object Oriented. Documentation is updated accordingly.

	VO.pm is added to access VO configuration and FQANs.

0.02    2012-06-07 15:55

	readconfig() returns a reference to the bound hash instead of
	a copy, so changes may be written back.

0.01    2012-06-01 23:41

        First version, unreleased

